title: Portland Exposé (1957 Film Noir) Directed by Harold D. Schuster | with Edward Binns

sources.title: Portland Exposé (1957 Film Noir) Directed by Harold D. Schuster | with Edward Binns
sources.description:
A tavern owner in mid-century Portland, Oregon finds the safety of himself and his family threatened when he becomes involved in a war between labor unions and a violent local crime syndicate.

Colorized version: https://youtu.be/fUyQvaXPwnk


Director: Harold D. Schuster
Writer: Jack DeWitt
Starring: Edward Binns, Carolyn Craig, Virginia Gregg, Jeanne Carmen
Genres: True Crime, Film-Noir, Mystery, Thriller
